==== 13 Feb 2015

NetUP Universal Dual DVB-CI FPGA firmware simulation
Universal card with two DVB-C, DVB-C2, DVB-T, DVB-T2, DVB-S, DVB-S2 inputs and two Common Interface slots. 
http://www.netup.tv/en-EN/netup-universal-dual-dvb-ci

FPGA: EP4CGX22CF19C8
Series: Cyclone IV GX
Number of Logic Elements/Cells: 21280
Total RAM Bits: 774144
Package: 324-FBGA (19x19)

==== Firmware simulation

* start modelsim
$ /mnt/sdb/altera/14.1/modelsim_ase/bin/vsim

* Open (File->Open) dvb_unici.mpf 

* In "Library" remove "work" and create it again (workaround)

* Run "Compile->Compile All"

* Choose Project (for example, "ci_control_tb") and run "Execute"

* Do simulation with "Simulate -> Run"
